3) Create category: 
Url: http://localhost:8080/categories/create

Request:

{
    "title": "Hotel",
    "description":"Un hostel es un tipo de alojamiento económico en el que poder compartir experiencias sociales.",
    "imageUrl": "https://unsplash.com/it/foto/WQJvWU_HZFo"
}

Response:

{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "Category created successfully",
    "data": null
}

4) Update category:
Url: http://localhost:8080/categories/update/1

Request:

{
    "title": "Casas",
    "description":"Un hotel es un establecimiento cuyo principal servicio es el hospedaje, ofreciendo a las personas cierto nivel de confort y seguridad durante sus estadías.",
    "imageUrl": "https://unsplash.com/it/foto/rlwE8f8anOc"
}

Response:

{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "Category updated successfully",
    "data": null
}

5) Delete category by Id:

Url: http://localhost:8080/categories/delete/1

Response:

{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "Category delete successful",
    "data": null
}




